00:37:47.910 --> 00:37:50.100
that I just passed around
if you got one yet.

00:37:50.100 --> 00:37:56.210
If you look at 3 sub 1 and look
down on it from the top

00:37:56.210 --> 00:38:02.140
and indicate the sense of
rotation that gets you from

00:38:02.140 --> 00:38:06.180
the one above to the one that's
directly below, your

00:38:06.180 --> 00:38:10.040
hand will curl around in
a clockwise fashion.

00:38:10.040 --> 00:38:14.440
And the little tails on the
symbol for the threefold axis

00:38:14.440 --> 00:38:18.770
trail out behind the way in
